To use the app:
1) Go to URL: 
2) You can add items via the add Item option
3) When you click on Paypal Checkout Page. You are redirected to a paypal login page. Use the 
Id: kripa211991-buyer-2@gmail.com
Password: testbuyer2
4) You can see the summary of your orders on the left side
5)_Click COntinue. You will be directed to a Payment Successful Page. Click 'Done'. It will show successful if finished.
6) Failure alerts will be thrown if any step fails.

Note: There is an issue with Cross Border Origin. To run it on chrome you will have to add --user-data-dir="C:/Chrome dev session" --disable-web-security in your chrome properties and run as adminstrator.

Note: Currently its only working on localhost. Can demo on my computer if needed.